<h3>What Does This Do?</h3>
<p>This module provides some Smarty utilities for use in pages of CMS Made Simple&trade; websites.</p>
<p>This module is a fork of <strong>CGSimpleSmarty</strong> developed by Robert Campbell.</p>
<p>Note: some javascript used in the help-system for this module assumes that the OneEleven admin theme is being used.</p>
